More than just a family tree

A tree, that binds the whole family together. In just a few minutes, you can order a very special present to someone you care about. Treecreate, a personal present of high quality and with special care for the environment.
get 10% discount on your first purchase, and have a chance to win a family tree!
When you give a Treecreate family tree, you can be sure to surprise your nearest every time. Your gift is completely unique to the person you give it to, and it does not get more personal.
Your Treecreate family tree is carefully carved in beautiful fragant oak wood with bark on top. it gives a natural expression as your thoughts are easily led to a lovely summerday with the family.
For each family tree you order from Treecreate, we plant a tree. That way we can help each other protect our nature and thereby make the world a greener place.

When we sendt your Treecreate family tree, it is carefully packed in strong FSC-certified re-use paper. In that way we secure that your valuable present is protected on the journey home, and we avoid using unnecessary plastic.
